2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper leverages machine learning-based scheduling search schemes to optimize computationally-intensive operators like convolution, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
3. cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) - The paper deals with optimizing CNN model inference on integrated GPUs, which is related to hardware architecture research. 
4. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper proposes an end-to-end solution for executing CNN model inference on integrated GPUs, which involves distributed and parallel computing. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses a solution for executing CNN model inference on integrated GPUs, which is related to systems and control research.
